│ Score: l2_distance(emb, FLOAT[3])                       │
│ Projections: id, sdb_inverted_index_score               │
│ Column Filter:                                          │
│ optional: Dynamic Filter (sdb_inverted_index_score < ?) │
│ ~4 rows                                                 │
╰─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯


